                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10051" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1146</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">329 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新学远大：可持续建筑中的原始创新实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Learn From BROAD’s Innovation:Original Innovation Practice in Sustainable Building</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑耀洲，褚鑫颖，李树文，汤一鹏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">远大科技集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">5 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">远大科技集团；原始创新；可持续建筑；远大活楼；2025百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Broad Technology Group, original innovation, sustainable architecture, values-driven, technology entrepreneurs</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业原始创新在国家创新驱动发展战略和新质生产力发展中占有突出地位，事关国计民生的建筑业，亟待通过原始创新实现从传统落后的建筑模式向未来可持续建筑模式的蜕变。“创新学远大”，被业界称为中国罕见的只搞原始创新的远大科技集团，用原始创新不断推动可持续建筑的革命。本案例首先通过考察团观看远大“活楼”建造视频及走访活楼工厂化预制生产流水线的情景，引入可持续建筑中的企业原始创新主题；随后，从原始创新的视角，简述远大企业背景；再后，重点以远大可持续建筑创新发展三个阶段：钢结构工厂化建筑——不锈钢芯板——不锈钢芯板建筑“千年活楼”为线索，详细描述了远大可持续建筑中的原始创新实践。本案例通过还原一个企业真实完整的原始创新实践全过程，能够帮助学生深化企业原始创新有关理论知识点的学习，问答“中国企业的原始创新到底怎样”的中国之问、世界之问、人民之问、时代之问，为中国企业的原始创新提供启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The original innovation of enterprises plays a prominent role in the national innovation strategy and the development of New Quality Productive Forces. The construction industry, which is crucial to the national economy and people’s livelihood, urgently needs to transform from the traditional and backward building model to the future sustainable building model through original innovation. “Learn from BROAD’s innovation”, BROAD Group, which is known in the industry as a rare Chinese enterprise that only engages in original innovation, continuously promotes the revolution of sustainable buildings with original innovation. This case first introduces the theme of corporate original innovation through the scenario of an inspection team visiting the factory-prefabricated production line of BROAD’s “Holon Building”; then, from the perspective of original innovation, briefly outlines the background of BROAD. Subsequently, focusing on the key events in the three stages of the innovative development of BROAD’s sustainable buildings: factory-made steel structure buildings-the B-CORE slab-the B-CORE slab building Millennium “Holon Building”, it details the original innovation practice in BROAD’s sustainable buildings. By restoring the entire real and complete process of an enterprise’s original innovation practice, this case can help students deepen their understanding of relevant theoretical knowledge about corporate original innovation, answer the questions of China, the world, the people, and the times regarding “what exactly is the original innovation of Chinese enterprises”, and provide inspiration for the original innovation of Chinese enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《科技创新》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">原始创新的概念和特征；原始创新的驱动因素；原始创新的实现路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
